g.text: Detect instances of PHI leaking through resource metadata, tags, and cloud logs.
Classify metadata risks based on PHI sensitivity and exposure potential.
Automate scans across infrastructure-as-code, logs, and APIs to flag violations.
Prevent future issues using tagging standards, policies, and CI/CD enforcement.
Clean up exposed metadata, re-encrypt resources, and correct IAM configurations.
Use AWS-native and third-party tools to detect future violations in real time.
